It seems live one of those tough choices: Spend precious time and money seeking out a cure for the cancerous tumor in your arm... or just amputate the entire limb? If you &quot;cure&quot; it, great... but there's the chance that the cancer has already spread. And who knows? It could pop up in your lungs in a month or two. It's a really tough decision, I think.<br>
