<br>
Now I ask you this, most of the people that I know that have lived through war, agree with the idea that killing innocent civilian should be avoided if possible.  You seem to think that it should be a requirement.  Jackass.  If the folks that have gone through hell feel that we can do something other than bomb civilians, why do you think we should?  Come out of your trailer park home and see the rest of the world.  America isn't the only place on the map.  The world is filled with people that live, love, feel pain and sorrow, have children and something watch them die.  You seem to think only Americans have these feelings, but all you do is reveal just how ignorant you are by what you say.  You somehow think America is so righteous... but have you ever asked the people that have served this country do they feel that way?  They know America has tons of dirty little secrets.  The politicans have bad reputations for a reason.<br>
<br>
Do I feel it's ok to see American soldiers die?  Nope.  But I'd rather see a MAN die instead of 100 innocent people.  Maybe you see a difference between Afghan people and American people, but I don't.  We are all people.  You say they hate America.  Well they have good reason to harbor those feelings.  Yeah I heard what the President said about the &quot;attack on Freedom&quot;... that's bullshit.  Think for yourself for a sec..wait... you're too stupid for that.  Well read a ... oops!  Another avenue you can't explore (I hear RIF works).  Well there must be something you can research to find out some info that isn't given on the idiot box.  Find it, and learn.<br>
<br>
In spite of all of that, I still love this country, and I wouldn't want to leave it.  Even so, I refuse to believe everything they tell me.  Don't forget, this is the same country that told Black people they are less than human.  This is the same country they nearly extermination the Native American for the good of said country.  This is the same country that placed thousands of Asian Americans in concentration camps during WWII.  This is the same country that trained many of the Bin Laden's associates in the art of assasination.  I refuse to blindly accept every tid of information that the American government and media gives me.  If America can target a person's home, and kill their family, without harming anyone else, (those that know will understand) we have to ability to target only the things that are necessary to bomb.<br>
<br>
I'm gonna close this now.  Please go back to the Trail park and watch Jerry Springer.  At least you could feel at home.<br>
